@page "/about"
@inject IJSRuntime JSRuntime

<PageTitle>About Us - RC Soil Solutions</PageTitle>

<!-- Page Header -->
<section class="page-header bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-right">
                <h1>About Us</h1>
                <p class="lead">Get to know the story, mission, and people behind RC Soil Solutions</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 text-md-end" data-aos="fade-left">
                <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
                    <ol class="breadcrumb justify-content-md-end">
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="" class="text-white">Home</a></li>
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item active text-white" aria-current="page">About Us</li>
                    </ol>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Company Story Section -->
<section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0" data-aos="fade-right">
                <img src="images/about-history.jpg" alt="RC Soil Solutions History" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-lg">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-left">
                <div class="section-title text-start">
                    <h2>Our Story</h2>
                </div>
                <p>RC Soil Solutions was founded in 2008 by Robert Campbell, a soil scientist with a passion for sustainable agriculture and land management. What began as a small consulting service has grown into a comprehensive soil solutions company serving agricultural, residential, and commercial clients across the region.</p>
                <p>Robert's vision was simple: to help landowners and farmers understand and improve their soil, using science-based methods that prioritize long-term sustainability. That vision remains at the heart of everything we do today.</p>
                <p>Over the past 15 years, we've expanded our services, built a team of experts, and developed proprietary soil treatment methods that have helped thousands of clients transform their land and increase productivity while maintaining environmental responsibility.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Mission & Values Section -->
<section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Our Mission & Values</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="section-subtitle">What drives us and shapes our approach to soil management</p>
        
        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-primary">Our Mission</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">To provide innovative, sustainable soil solutions that enhance land productivity, promote environmental stewardship, and empower our clients to achieve their goals through healthy soil management.</p>
                        <p class="card-text">We believe that healthy soil is the foundation for a healthy ecosystem, successful agriculture, and beautiful landscapes. Our mission is to help our clients understand and improve their soil in ways that benefit both their immediate goals and the long-term health of the environment.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-primary">Our Values</h3>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li class="mb-3">
                                <h5><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i> Scientific Excellence</h5>
                                <p>We base our recommendations and solutions on sound scientific principles and the latest research.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li class="mb-3">
                                <h5><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i> Sustainability</h5>
                                <p>We prioritize long-term soil health and environmental sustainability in all our practices.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li class="mb-3">
                                <h5><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i> Integrity</h5>
                                <p>We operate with honesty, transparency, and ethical conduct in all our business dealings.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <h5><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i> Client Partnership</h5>
                                <p>We work closely with our clients, treating their land and goals with the same care and attention we would our own.</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

